name: Geekbench: Photo Filter
description: Applies colour and blur filters, level adjustments, cropping, scaling, and image compositing filters to 10 photos range in size from 3 MP to 15 MPThe score is calibrated against a baseline score of 2,500 (Dell Precision 3460 with a Core i7-12700 processor) as per the Geekbench 6 Benchmark Internals.
